  "description": "A panoramic view of a sprawling cityscape meeting the coast, bathed in the soft light of a cloudy day. The foreground is dominated by a dense urban landscape of houses and buildings, transitioning to a calm coastline with a long bridge stretching across the water. In the distance, rolling hills and mountains form a hazy backdrop. A dramatic patch of sunlight breaks through the clouds, illuminating a small area above the bridge, creating a focal point in the sky. The overall composition evokes a sense of scale and tranquility.",
